{"tid":31984,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"俏女郎爬梯落簷篷勇救百厭貓咪（有圖）","createTime":"2016-12-10T03:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T10:50:24.000Z","uid":43678,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6447f8c386c4fa2538cb114ebd0b74460c786283","tid":31984,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:18:13.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=4iEQhx3xGX3T5lmh166FkwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=74106055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】旺角鬧市上演一幕豔麗溫情救貓場面。一隻約2歲大貪玩小家貓，疑被街景吸引，昨晚10時許，於通菜街39號一樓一間賓館的露台爬落約8呎以下簷篷，牠無大礙，惟「有落無上」當場被困，適逢一名20餘歲，樣貌俏麗甜美，曾多次勇救小動物的愛心爆棚女子，到賓館探訪貓咪的女主人，她見狀立即報案求助。 <br />\n<br />\n俏女郎爬梯落簷篷　勇救百厭貓咪笑開眉<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=4iEQhx3xGX3T5lmh166FkwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=74106055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】旺角鬧市上演一幕豔麗溫情救貓場面。一隻約2歲大貪玩小家貓，疑被街景吸引，昨晚10時許，於通菜街39號一樓一間賓館的露台爬落約8呎以下簷篷，牠無大礙，惟「有落無上」當場被困，適逢一名20餘歲，樣貌俏麗甜美，曾多次勇救小動物的愛心爆棚女子，到賓館探訪貓咪的女主人，她見狀立即報案求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場了解情況後，通知愛協人員協助。其後愛協人員亦抵埗，視察現場環境後，將一把長梯放於簷篷，由於考慮到簷篷承受重力有限，並擔心貓咪見到陌生人受驚亂竄，會導致受傷甚至墮樓，到訪女子遂主動請纓親身營救。她接受愛協人員為其做足安全措施，戴上厚手套及將一條安全繩索繫於身上後，小心翼翼爬到簷篷，將貓咪擁入懷中；貓咪亦乖乖就範，再由愛協人員放下一個貓籠，女子將貓咪放入貓籠後，交由愛協人員放回賓館安全位置，物歸原主。俏女子及後亦動作俐落爬回賓館，她見貓咪由她安全救回，亦笑逐顏開。<br />\n<br />\n救貓女子姓巫，她表示自己平日也經常當動物義工，曾於內地救過不少貓狗，亦曾在北角遇到受傷的野豬，她最終成功將野豬救離險境，交由相關部門處理善後。巫亦透露，獲救貓咪的女主人養有多隻可愛小貓，她對是次能親身救回該隻貓咪，大感安慰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcxty0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhcxty0q.jpg&h=7129baa2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LP3CeV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLP3CeV7.jpg&h=a2ebd3c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/mobile/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161210%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001.html&d=4iEQhx3xGX3T5lmh166FkwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=4ef6d3b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161210/mobile/bkn-20161210001415581-1210_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9572c201bbb744cc6a6e15eaf51dde4c611d1149","tid":31984,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5ff1cd9ac37b69ff61f5d2be96f08eff96fdfbd","tid":31984,"uid":1539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1828c52775f170ef2d2aec8f69b56062fc54ee","tid":31984,"uid":130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:19:43.000Z","msg":"波大心地好"},{"pid":"4ff74da65d6c9fa2dd69dcf0d85abe32033c2bfb","tid":31984,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"毒撚被困 你估有無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ce6a18f8610375d28466b3caed034a268b8b7df4","tid":31984,"uid":678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁撚大包米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f95e12bf73cb8be37b7fc573837d24af33c8f3","tid":31984,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:20:56.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪做緊show<img src=\"/assets/f